'fore you come back. okay?

504
00:32:57.935 --> 00:32:58.936
How 'bout that?

505
00:32:59.019 --> 00:33:00.270
Mm-hmm.

506
00:33:00.354 --> 00:33:02.314
I'm gonna…

507
00:33:02.398 --> 00:33:04.608
I'm gonna be right outside.
baby. okay?

508
00:33:06.568 --> 00:33:07.695
- Okay.
- 'Kay.

509
00:33:10.072 --> 00:33:11.740
Oh. my God!

510
00:33:12.908 --> 00:33:16.286
Sorry about that. She…
She gets worked up over the kids.

511
00:33:16.370 --> 00:33:18.414
I'm Mexican. No explanation needed.

512
00:33:19.957 --> 00:33:21.625
I need a minute alone with Cooper.

513
00:33:22.084 --> 00:33:23.627
Yeah. I should get back to my son.

514
00:33:25.254 --> 00:33:26.505
Call me if you need anything.

515
00:33:26.588 --> 00:33:27.965
I'll be back tomorrow.

516
00:33:28.048 --> 00:33:29.091
Thank you.

517
00:33:36.557 --> 00:33:37.933
Nothing's going on.

518
00:33:39.351 --> 00:33:41.186
Her husband just died.

519
00:33:42.771 --> 00:33:43.897
I'm trying…

520
00:33:45.190 --> 00:33:47.359
She called and asked for help.
and I gave it.

521
00:33:47.443 --> 00:33:49.111
She's not my concern. You are.

522
00:33:50.654 --> 00:33:52.322
And at the moment.

523
00:33:52.406 --> 00:33:55.451
the fuckers that put you
in this hospital are my main concern.

524
00:33:55.534 --> 00:33:57.035
If my father steps in…

525
00:33:57.119 --> 00:33:58.829
This is not your dad talking.

526
00:33:58.912 --> 00:34:01.206
This is the general manager
of an oil company talking.

527
00:34:01.290 --> 00:34:04.084
And when my employees
break into another employee's

528
00:34:04.168 --> 00:34:05.711
company-provided housing

529
00:34:05.794 --> 00:34:07.796
and beat the dog shit out of him
to the point where a surgeon

530
00:34:07.880 --> 00:34:10.257
has to re-inflate his lung. I step in.

531
00:34:13.218 --> 00:34:15.471
Manuel and Antonio.

532
00:34:16.096 --> 00:34:17.264
Who else?

533
00:34:20.476 --> 00:34:23.479
You can tell me.
or I'll beat it out of the first two.

534
00:34:27.107 --> 00:34:28.317
I don't know their names.

535
00:34:30.569 --> 00:34:32.446
Maintenance crew
for the buffalo field.

536
00:34:34.448 --> 00:34:35.824
That's all you had to say.

537
00:34:37.576 --> 00:34:39.703
You're gonna have to move slow
with this girl.

538
00:34:41.789 --> 00:34:43.665
She's hurting in a way
that you can't understand.

539
00:34:43.749 --> 00:34:45.667
and she's trying to find
somewhere to put it.

540
00:34:46.543 --> 00:34:48.003
It's not like that.

541
00:34:48.086 --> 00:34:49.296
How many other widows do you think

542
00:34:49.379 --> 00:34:51.632
are sitting in this hospital tonight
with their helpers?

543
00:34:58.639 --> 00:35:01.183
This ain't the first time
you took a beating over this girl.

544
00:35:02.476 --> 00:35:05.145
This is the kind of beating you get
when the first one didn't take.

545
00:35:11.360 --> 00:35:14.279
- Yeah?
- He just got to his trailer.

546
00:35:14.363 --> 00:35:15.531
<i>Alone?</i>

547
00:35:15.614 --> 00:35:16.782
With his roommate.

548
00:35:16.865 --> 00:35:18.742
<i>All right. I want you
to turn those cameras off</i>

549
00:35:18.826 --> 00:35:21.286
and don't cut 'em back on
till I tell you. all right?

550
00:35:21.370 --> 00:35:22.538
Yes. sir.

551
00:35:27.209 --> 00:35:28.836
Can we talk to him now?

552
00:35:29.378 --> 00:35:33.006
No need. Meet me at the man camp.
Give me a ten minute head start.

553
00:35:43.809 --> 00:35:47.104
I'm really relaxed now.
Can I go see him?

554
00:35:47.187 --> 00:35:48.647
He's all yours.

555
00:35:49.606 --> 00:35:50.858
You got plans tonight?

556
00:35:51.400 --> 00:35:53.777
- Soon as you give 'em to me.
- Let's go.

557
00:35:54.319 --> 00:35:56.113
Hey. don't let her drive.

558
00:36:02.077 --> 00:36:03.203
Mm.

559
00:36:38.739 --> 00:36:39.740
You want something?

560
00:36:41.700 --> 00:36:42.951
Don't leave home without it.

561
00:36:47.289 --> 00:36:48.624
We might not even get to use it.

562
00:36:54.880 --> 00:36:56.465
You should just
cut that fucking thing off.

563
00:36:57.215 --> 00:36:58.717
Ain't your hand that got smashed.

564
00:37:03.847 --> 00:37:06.350
- You got a bitch coming over?
- Not till I get paid.

565
00:37:11.146 --> 00:37:13.398
Fuck. It's the boss.

566
00:37:14.608 --> 00:37:16.693
Don't answer. Make like we're asleep.

567
00:37:16.777 --> 00:37:18.278
I can fucking hear you.

568
00:37:24.826 --> 00:37:26.703
What's up?

569
00:37:35.003 --> 00:37:36.672
This seem familiar. motherfucker?

570
00:37:41.510 --> 00:37:42.511
Hey. man…

571
00:37:52.312 --> 00:37:55.357
You get on your fucking phone
and call your friends.

572
00:37:55.440 --> 00:37:57.275
You know. the ones that you called

573
00:37:57.359 --> 00:37:59.194
that put my fucking son
in the hospital.

574
00:38:02.906 --> 00:38:04.116
No?

575
00:38:04.199 --> 00:38:06.076
He don't want to call
his friends. Boss.

576
00:38:06.159 --> 00:38:07.911
Me and my boys will
take him in the back.

577
00:38:07.995 --> 00:38:09.287
Okay. I'd appreciate that.

578
00:38:09.371 --> 00:38:10.414
Oh. we'll convince you.

579
00:38:10.497 --> 00:38:11.540
- Come on.
- No. No. fuck.

580
00:38:13.333 --> 00:38:14.543
Let's talk.

581
00:38:15.043 --> 00:38:16.044
No!

582
00:38:21.925 --> 00:38:24.636
Nobody said get up. Manny.

583
00:38:32.728 --> 00:38:34.312
Have a seat. Manuel.

584
00:38:41.903 --> 00:38:43.530
Here's how this is gonna go.

585
00:38:43.613 --> 00:38:45.073
Needless to say. you're fired.

586
00:38:45.574 --> 00:38:48.118
By noon tomorrow.
you'll be on a "no hire" list

587
00:38:48.201 --> 00:38:50.746
for every fucking oil company
in the Permian Basin.

588
00:38:50.829 --> 00:38:52.664
Sheriff's gonna be here
in about five minutes.

589
00:38:52.748 --> 00:38:54.708
and he's gonna toss
this fucking place.

590
00:38:54.791 --> 00:38:59.212
And I'm just guessing he'll add
felon in possession of a firearm.

591
00:38:59.296 --> 00:39:01.381
possession of a controlled substance.

592
00:39:01.465 --> 00:39:04.301
and maybe possession of
a controlled substance

593
00:39:04.384 --> 00:39:06.344
with intent to distribute.

594
00:39:06.428 --> 00:39:09.765
And any goddamn one of those
violates your parole.

595
00:39:10.724 --> 00:39:12.517
And then. you add on top of that shit.

596
00:39:12.601 --> 00:39:15.520
aggravated assault charge
and kidnapping.

597
00:39:15.604 --> 00:39:17.773
'cause when you shut the door on him.

598
00:39:17.856 --> 00:39:19.024
that's kidnapping.

599
00:39:20.567 --> 00:39:22.778
I ain't a goddamn mathematician.

600
00:39:22.861 --> 00:39:24.404
but that's. like. 30 years.

601
00:39:25.572 --> 00:39:27.949
That's what I do to people
who hurt my family.

602
00:39:28.033 --> 00:39:30.202
You fucked with the wrong hillbilly.

603
00:39:34.289 --> 00:39:37.084
I'm gonna take 30 years
of your life away from you.

604
00:39:38.001 --> 00:39:39.920
And if you ever come back
to this place.

605
00:39:40.921 --> 00:39:42.214
I'm gonna take the rest of it.

606
00:39:48.804 --> 00:39:50.180
Have you met the sheriff?

607
00:39:50.263 --> 00:39:52.682
Stand up and turn around.

608
00:39:57.687 --> 00:40:00.148
They're having a confession
in the back room.

609
00:40:01.650 --> 00:40:02.943
Tommy.

610
00:40:04.361 --> 00:40:06.988
- Did he have anything to say?
- He gave up the names.

611
00:40:07.739 --> 00:40:09.407
Even wrote 'em down for you.

612
00:40:09.491 --> 00:40:11.201
You think he'd repeat 'em to me?

613
00:40:11.284 --> 00:40:12.619
Sure he would if you asked.

614
00:40:20.335 --> 00:40:22.587
Would you confirm the names
of the other assailants?

615
00:40:24.131 --> 00:40:25.674
You… You gonna take me with you?

616
00:40:26.633 --> 00:40:28.093
Well. that depends.

617
00:40:28.176 --> 00:40:29.845
You gonna say something
give me a reason?

618
00:40:31.555 --> 00:40:32.764
I'll give you a reason.

619
00:40:33.223 --> 00:40:34.516
You boys give us a minute?

620
00:40:56.204 --> 00:40:58.081
Haven't done anything
like that since…

621
00:41:00.333 --> 00:41:01.710
2016.

622
00:41:05.881 --> 00:41:07.424
Place is getting wild again.

623
00:41:13.555 --> 00:41:15.974
I got to get my boy out of here
before somebody kills him.

624
00:41:18.018 --> 00:41:19.811
Nah. we run the killers off.

625
00:41:23.773 --> 00:41:26.318
There's something about that boy.
just draws trouble to him

626
00:41:26.401 --> 00:41:27.944
like bugs to a light.

627
00:41:32.866 --> 00:41:34.701
He ain't mean enough
for this place. Dale.

628
00:41:47.714 --> 00:41:49.216
He just ain't mean enough.

629
00:41:56.348 --> 00:42:01.144
<i>There's no shame
in being broken-hearted</i>

630
00:42:03.813 --> 00:42:09.152
<i>Though I try to do more to fix my soul</i>

631
00:42:11.821 --> 00:42:15.951
<i>I'm trying to be more
than when I started</i>

632
00:42:18.411 --> 00:42:21.581
<i>There's no path before me</i>

633
00:43:05.625 --> 00:43:06.626
English — SDH

633
